text FuchsiaCity_SafariZone_Entrance_Text_ExplainSafariZone {
    format("The SAFARI ZONE actually has four zones in it.\p Each zone has different kinds of POKéMON, even some rare ones.\p Use the supplied SAFARI BALLS to catch them.\p You can also throw BAIT or ROCKS besides the SAFARI BALLS.\p If you throw BAIT, the POKéMON becomes less likely to flee, but\l harder to catch.\p If you throw ROCKS, the POKéMON becomes more likely to flee, but\l easier to catch.\p When you run out of time or SAFARI BALLS, it's game over for you!")
}

